title: Best Bits with Raymundo: PART 1
itunes:title: Best Bits with Raymundo: PART 1
description:
Morgan and Raymundo talked about life at their homes and their weird food habits. Raymundo shared the latest life news with him and his wife, and Morgan recalled past memories she can’t believe she forgot. Raymundo helps Morgan find her stage name, and they discuss Halloween plans and costumes.
